PlugAuth-Plugin-AD version 0.01
===============================

This is a back end module for PlugAuth to authenticate users 
with MS Windows Active Directory

It's based on Graham Ollis PlugAuth::Plugin::LDAP.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

